{"TopicId":91401,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Using throttle with Mouse Wheel ..??","CreatedByName":"TheGuruGame","CreatedById":125168,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T17:25:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TheGuruGame","CreatedById":125168,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T17:25:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI dont know what you guys think of it, but i think using my mousewheel as throttle is OP\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spartwo","CreatedById":58131,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T18:42:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI love this idea.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T18:46:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow would it be OP?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd how would I zoom the view? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"andrew123","CreatedById":46719,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T18:51:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHow would it be OP?\u003Cp\u003EAnd how would I zoom the view? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA second mouse? XD\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T21:50:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EPerhaps a modifier key? Alt\u002Bmouse wheel could operate the throttle, and zooming the view would happen as normal when not holding Alt.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheGuruGame","CreatedById":125168,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T23:26:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHow would it be OP?\u003Cp\u003EAnd how would I zoom the view? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMaybe shift \u002B scroll for zooming.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBut having scroll for throttle could improve response.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T00:13:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBut then you accidentally don\u0027t hold the shift key down enough, and you lose the last of your fuel. And then remember that Shift currently does throttle, and... Well, anyway, I don\u0027t like this idea.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T01:52:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENoooo! There\u0027s too many functions tied to the mousewheel already, makes KSP a pain on a laptop at times.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E(Seriously, the controls should be more laptop-friendly, laptops are the most popular form factor sold today.)\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}